  <ThingDef ParentName="BaseSkynet">
    <defName>Skynet_Terminatrix</defName>
    <label>Terminatrix</label>
    <description>The Terminatrix (T-X) is designed to not only terminate humans but also rogue Terminators that were reprogrammed by the Resistance. The T-X is an "anti-terminator terminator". T-X uses a composite of the T-800 and T-1000, which is a solid endoskeleton covered with a liquid metal "mimetic polyalloy." This allows it to take the shape of any humanoid that it touches. It is possible to remove the mimetic polyalloy from the endoskeleton by using the immensely strong magnetic force from a cyclic particle accelerator.</description>
